    "details": {
      "cr": 8,
      "type": {
        "value": "undead"
      },
      "alignment": "lawful evil",
      "biography": {
        "value": "\n                        Once a brilliant and ambitious wizard, this individual delved too deep into forbidden magic in pursuit of immortality. Through dark rituals and a pact with fell entities, they achieved lichdom, shedding their mortal coil to become a being of pure arcane power and malice. Now, they seek to amass forbidden knowledge and spread their corrupting influence across the land.\n                        <hr>\n                        <p><strong>Behavior:</strong> The lich is a master manipulator, preferring to use its minions and magical traps to deal with threats. It will only engage directly when absolutely necessary, unleashing its most devastating spells and abilities to crush its enemies. Its primary goal is the acquisition of more power and the perfection of its dark magic.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Appearance:</strong> A skeletal figure draped in decaying, ornate robes. Its empty eye sockets glow with malevolent green energy, and wisps of dark energy emanate from its desiccated form. It carries a gnarled staff crackling with arcane power.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Twist:</strong> The lich's phylactery is not a hidden object, but rather a sentient creature it has bound to its soul, making its destruction a moral quandary for those who discover it.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Habitat:</strong> Unknown</p>\n                        <p><strong>Treasure:</strong> The lich possesses a hoard of ancient tomes, arcane components, jeweled artifacts, and a significant amount of gold and precious gems.</p>\n                    "
      },
      "race": "Lich"
    },
